{"tid":545284,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣落雨可以去邊好","createTime":"2018-01-30T11:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T08:29:05.000Z","uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3e28db7942eff01da397168bd1aae2b9009add62","tid":545284,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T11:11:48.000Z","msg":"黎左幾日台北 除左第一日好天少少<br />\n第二日開始落狗屎又凍<br />\n本身諗住聽日出發去花蓮 落雨到底仲去唔去好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔想繼續留係台北 <br />\n有無巴絲可以建議我去邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申咩都無book定 下星期一返香港"},{"pid":"29d130f7875314b2e89933f90ececb672eabf7c9","tid":545284,"uid":165202,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"我都係下星期一返<br />\n要結個伴嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e21ff13ebde8707810c41b75e3525297f85f8f","tid":545284,"uid":72269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:23:28.000Z","msg":"但去到花蓮落雨咪慘過留喺台北<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bf1d25ad9bb3bce13fb75bca418134a0d5922d","tid":545284,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T02:52:44.000Z","msg":"上次去花蓮都係落狗屎<br />\n大半日都留係民宿<br />\n夜晚頂唔順出去行下<br />\n結果成身濕曬<br />\n<br />\n不過我明既<br />\n花蓮點都好過係台北<br />\n因為台北太似香港&hellip;"},{"pid":"e247ae4cff9bae8c32f3bc2e3de386a719ba6ebc","tid":545284,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:04:46.000Z","msg":"台北而家只係毛毛雨，仲可以周圍行下<br />\n如果唔怕遠，鐘意影相，可以坐火車去基蘭、福隆、宜蘭"},{"pid":"513541dc5d520ed4f4403aa0af5215b8660d52a4","tid":545284,"uid":147988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係下星期一返<br />\n要結個伴嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma